<b><a href="/wiki/Controversies_related_to_Islam_and_Muslims" title="Controversies related to Islam and Muslims">Controversies related to Islam and Muslims</a></b></span><br /></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="2" style="font-size: 90%; background-color:rgb(230 230 250); border-top:1px #686; background:#C0C0C0;"><b>Criticism of Islam</b></td>
</tr>
